<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rick and Morty Quiz</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Rick and Morty Quiz</h1>

    <form id="quizForm" action="/quiz/submit" method="post" onsubmit="return confirm('Вы уверены, что хотите отправить викторину?');">
        <ol class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <p>Какая марка кроссовок является самой популярной?</p>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q1" value="a" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">а) Nike</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q1" value="b" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">б) Adidas</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q1" value="c" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">в) Reebok</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q1" value="d" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">г) Puma</label>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li class="list-group-item">
                <p>Какая модель кроссовок считается классикой?</p>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q2" value="a" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">а) Nike Air Force 1</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q2" value="b" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">б) Adidas Superstar</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q2" value="c" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">в) Converse Chuck Taylor</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q2" value="d" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">г) Reebok Classic</label>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li class="list-group-item">
                <p>Какая марка выпускает кроссовки с технологией Boost?</p>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q3" value="a" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">а) Nike</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q3" value="b" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">б) Adidas</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q3" value="c" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">в) Puma</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q3" value="d" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">г) Reebok</label>
                </div>
            </li>

            <li class="list-group-item">
                <p>Какая модель кроссовок ассоциируется с баскетболистом Майклом Джорданом?</p>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q4" value="a" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">а) Nike Air Max</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q4" value="b" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">б) Adidas Yeezy</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q4" value="c" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">в) Nike Air Jordan</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input type="radio" name="q4" value="d" class="form-check-input">
                    <label class="form-check-label">г) Reebok Pump</label>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Отправить</button>
    </form>


    <div id="timer" class="mt-4">Осталось времени: <span id="countdown">30</span> секунд</div>
</div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

<script>
    let countdown = 30;
    const countdownElement = document.getElementById('countdown');
    const timerElement = document.getElementById('timer');

    const timer = setInterval(() => {
        countdown--;
        countdownElement.textContent = countdown;

        if (countdown <= 0) {
            clearInterval(timer);
            timerElement.textContent = 'Время вышло! Отправка викторины...';
            document.getElementById('quizForm').submit();
        }
    }, 1000);
</script>
</body>
</html>